ies-5-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-5-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-5-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eCheesy Pizza Fries\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"97530\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 6\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e35\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e45\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003ePizza fries are our new favorite thing!! Crispy waffle fries topped with marinara, melty mozzarella and pepperoni. The parmesan and fresh basil take it over the top. So cheesy, crisp and satisfying! Best game day snack ever.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97530\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 \u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e(20-ounce) bag\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e frozen waffle fries\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounces\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eshredded mozzarella/provolone/italian blend cheese\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/rao-39-s-homemade-marinara-sauce-premium-quality-all-natural-tomato-sauce-38-pasta-sauce-keto-friendly-38-carb-conscious-24oz/-/A-13349580?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003emarinara sauce,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eor more if desired\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e⅓\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003emini pepperoni\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/ground-italian-seasoning-0-75oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77587153?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eitalian seasoning\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/kraft-100-grated-parmesan-cheese-8oz/-/A-12958582?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efinely grated parmesan cheese,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-basil-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495109?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efresh basil,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003epinch\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/crushed-red-pepper-1-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77584991?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ecrushed red pepper flakes\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"97530\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97530-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreheat the oven to 450 degrees F. Line a baking sheet with parchment paper.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97530-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSpread the fries in a single layer on the baking sheet. Bake for 20 to 25 minutes, or until crispy and crunchy.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97530-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eRemove the fries and top with half of the shredded cheese. Drizzle on some marinara sauce, all over the cheese. Add the pepperoni, remaining cheese and italian seasoning.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97530-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eReturn the pan to the oven for 5 to 10 minutes, just until the cheese melts and the pepperoni is crispy.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-97530-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSprinkling all over with parmesan cheese and the fresh basil. Top with pepper flakes if desired. Serve immediately!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAppetizer, Snack\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"pizza fries\" width=\"1589\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/01/pizza-fries/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Cheesy Pizza Fries.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-scaled.jpg 1589w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-728x1008.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-768x1063.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-1109x1536.jpg 1109w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-1479x2048.jpg 1479w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-150x208.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1589px) 100vw, 1589px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201589%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-scaled.jpg 1589w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-728x1008.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-768x1063.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-1109x1536.jpg 1109w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-1479x2048.jpg 1479w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-150x208.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/pizza-fries-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCheese = happiness.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\u003c/article\u003e \n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
